After 21.5 years, we have decided with a heavy heart to stop as BT. A decision that has been coming for some time, but which we have been able to postpone through various efforts in recent years. And so we have to be honest, to ourselves and to the club. We do it with full dedication, or we don't do it at all. This is the reason why we have made the decision to put an end to BT after this season. Of course, this does not mean that we will no longer be seen at De Spinnekop or during away matches.
